<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Informasi Akun Anda</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4;">
    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 40px 20px;">
        <tr>
            <td align="center">
                <table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
                    
                    <!-- Header -->
                    <tr>
                        <td style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); padding: 40px 30px; text-align: center;">
                            <h1 style="margin: 0; color: #ffffff; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 600;">
                                üéâ Selamat Datang!
                            </h1>
                            <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #ffffff; font-size: 16px; opacity: 0.9;">
                                Akun Anda telah berhasil didaftarkan
                            </p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <!-- Content -->
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 40px 30px;">
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0; color: #333333; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
                                Halo <strong>{{employeeName}}</strong>,
                            </p>
                            
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 30px 0; color: #666666; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">
                                Akun Anda di sistem kami telah berhasil dibuat. Berikut adalah kredensial login Anda:
                            </p>

                            <!-- Credential Box -->
                            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px; border: 2px solid #e9ecef; margin-bottom: 30px;">
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="padding: 25px;">
                                        
                                        <!-- Company Name -->
                                        <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                                            <tr>
                                                <td>
                                                    <p style="margin: 0 0 5px 0; font-size: 12px; color: #666666; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; font-weight: 600;">
                                                        Company Name
                                                    </p>
                                                    <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 18px; color: #333333; font-weight: 600; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 12px; border-radius: 5px; border-left: 4px solid #667eea;">
                                                        {{companyName}}
                                                    </p>
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
                                        </table>


                                        <!-- Company Code -->
                                        <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                                            <tr>
                                                <td>
                                                    <p style="margin: 0 0 5px 0; font-size: 12px; color: #666666; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; font-weight: 600;">
                                                        Company Code
                                                    </p>
                                                    <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 18px; color: #333333; font-weight: 600; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 12px; border-radius: 5px; border-left: 4px solid #667eea;">
                                                        {{companyCode}}
                                                    </p>
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
                                        </table>

                                        <!-- Username -->
                                        <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                                            <tr>
                                                <td>
                                                    <p style="margin: 0 0 5px 0; font-size: 12px; color: #666666; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; font-weight: 600;">
                                                        Employee Username
                                                    </p>
                                                    <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 18px; color: #333333; font-weight: 600; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 12px; border-radius: 5px; border-left: 4px solid #667eea;">
                                                        {{employeeUsername}}
                                                    </p>
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
                                        </table>

                                        <!-- Password -->
                                        <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                                            <tr>
                                                <td>
                                                    <p style="margin: 0 0 5px 0; font-size: 12px; color: #856404; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; font-weight: 700;">
                                                        ‚ö†Ô∏è Password
                                                    </p>
                                                    <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 18px; color: #333333; font-weight: 600; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; background-color: #fff3cd; padding: 12px; border-radius: 5px; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;">
                                                        {{password}}
                                                    </p>
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
                                        </table>

                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>

                            <!-- Security Notice -->
                            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #e7f3ff; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #2196F3; margin-bottom: 30px;">
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="padding: 20px;">
                                        <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #1976D2; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600;">
                                            üîí Catatan Keamanan Penting:
                                        </p>
                                        <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #1976D2; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8;">
                                            <li>Simpan informasi ini dengan aman</li>
                                            <li>Segera ubah password setelah login pertama kali</li>
                                            <li>Jangan bagikan kredensial Anda kepada siapa pun</li>
                                            <li>Gunakan kombinasi password yang kuat</li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>

                            <!-- Login Button -->
                            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                                <tr>
                                    <td align="center" style="padding: 10px 0;">
                                        <a href="{{loginUrl}}" style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 15px 40px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);">
                                            üöÄ Login Sekarang
                                        </a>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>

                            <p style="margin: 30px 0 0 0; color: #999999; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; text-align: center;">
                                Jika Anda mengalami kesulitan atau memiliki pertanyaan, silakan hubungi tim support kami di <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" style="color: #667eea; text-decoration: none;">{{supportEmail}}</a>
                            </p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <!-- Footer -->
                    <tr>
                        <td style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;">
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #666666; font-size: 14px;">
                                {{companyName}}
                            </p>
                            <p style="margin: 0; color: #999999; font-size: 12px;">
                                ¬© {{year}} All rights reserved
                            </p>
                            <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #999999; font-size: 12px;">
                                Email ini dikirim secara otomatis. Mohon tidak membalas email ini.
                            </p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>